nodes.text: Star Wars: TIE Fighter Deluxe Book and Model Set

Star Wars: TIE Fighter Deluxe Book and Model Set is a TIE/ln space superiority starfighter model kit published by Insight Editions as part of their IncrediBuilds collection. The kit includes a laser-cut, FSC-certified wood sheet, step-by-step instructions, coloring and crafting ideas, and a TIE Fighter guidebook, titled Inside the Empire's Winged Menace, written by Michael Kogge. It was released on June 28, 2016.
